1. cd to postgres-prometheus-grafana dir
2. run command in terminal => docker-compose-v1 up -d
3. for the Prometheus dash, navigate to localhost://9090
4. for raw metrics, checkout localhost://9090/metrics and localhost://9187/metrics
5. to access Grafana, navigate to localhost://3000, username and password are admin
6. pull up postgres dashboard
7. close docker-compose image => docker-compose-v1 down